! Terminology

* [[BCC|https://github.com/iovisor/bcc]]: BPF Compiler Collection. `libbcc`.
* BPF: Berkeley Packet Filter. `libbpf`.
* [[bpftrace|https://github.com/iovisor/bpftrace]]: a newer front end that provides a special-purpose, high-level language for developing BPF tools.
* BTF: BPF Type Format. 
* eBPF: extended BPF.
* XDP: eXpress Data Path.

